import { INCREMENT, DECREMENT } from '../constant'
export default function countReducer(preStore, action) {
    const { type, data } = action
    switch (type) {
        case INCREMENT:
            return preStore + data
        case DECREMENT:
            return preStore - data
        default:
            return 0
    }
}
